<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>专转 驻专驻</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #fff; padding: 20px; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; }
        .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 20px; }
        .btn-meet { background: #1a73e8; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 1.2rem; display: inline-block; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .card { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; margin-top: 30px; }
        input { padding: 10px; width: 100%; max-width: 300px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px; }
        button { padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 4px; border: none; cursor: pointer; }
        .save { background: #1a73e8; color: white; }
        .danger { background: white; color: red; border: 1px solid red; margin-top: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h2>, <%= user.name %></h2>
        <a href="/logout" style="color: #5f6368; text-decoration: none;">爪</a>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 60px 0;">
        <h1> 驻砖?</h1>
        <p>爪专 驻砖 砖 砖转祝 转 拽砖专 注 砖转转驻</p>
        <br>
        <a href="/create-meeting" class="btn-meet"> 驻砖 砖</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h3>锔 专转 砖</h3>
        <form action="/update-profile" method="POST">
            <label>砖:</label><br>
            <input type="text" name="name" value="<%= user.name %>" required><br>
            <label>:</label><br>
            <input type="email" name="email" value="<%= user.email %>" required><br>
            <label>住住 砖 (驻爪):</label><br>
            <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="砖专 专拽   砖"><br>
            <button type="submit" class="save">砖专 砖</button>
        </form>
        
        <br><hr><br>
        
        <form action="/delete-account" method="POST" onsubmit="return confirm('? 驻注 转 驻!');">
            <button type="submit" class="danger"> 拽 转 砖 砖</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
